# CoreX events - sqs

This package provides an implementation of the CoreX events interface for sqs.

## Installation
~~~bash
pip install corex-events-sqs
~~~

## Usage
~~~python
from corex_events_sqs.handler import SqsHandler
handler = SqsHandler()
handler.example_method()
~~~
